ZH: 我们在大山里风餐露宿了三天。
EN: We camped in the mountains for three days.
ZH: 他们在台风袭来时只能风餐露宿。
EN: They had to camp out during the typhoon.
ZH: 她们决定风餐露宿，以便更快到达目的地。
EN: They decided to camp out in order to reach their destination faster.
ZH: 要是风餐露宿，就得准备好足够的食物和水。
EN: If you are going to camp out, you need to be prepared with enough food and water.
ZH: 这次旅行计划好好享受大自然，不会在宾馆住宿，要风餐露宿。
EN: This trip is planned to fully enjoy nature, not staying in hotels, but to camp out.
ZH: 在荒野中风餐露宿需要特别注意野生动物的出没。
EN: Camping out in the wilderness requires special attention to the presence of wild animals.
